pageProduct.name: QV Intensive Moisturiser 450G
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Soothing moisturiser for extremely dry and sensitive skin. This highly emollient intensive balm not only helps to rehydrate your skin, it also helps to seal in moisture to your skin.

Warnings

CAUTION:
Avoid eyes.  For external use only.  Store below 30°C.
Always read the label. Use only as directed.
If symptoms persist please see your healthcare professional.

Common Uses

• Water-free formulation won’t sting when applied to inflamed or cracked skin.
• Suitable for dry, sensitive, itchy skin.
• Low-irritant formulation, free from fragrance, colour and lanolin to suit sensitive skin types.
• Helps to maintain skin's protective properties.

Ingredients

Paraffinum Liquidum, Isopropyl Myristate, Petrolatum, Polyethylene, Cetearyl Alcohol, Silica, Dimethicone, BHT

Directions

Apply liberally to the face and body and massage in gently. Use after bathing and showering.
